                              IRTS.CodegenC, IRTS.Defunctionalise, IRTS.Inliner,
                              IRTS.Compiler, IRTS.CodegenJava, IRTS.BCImp,
                              IRTS.CodegenJavaScript,
                              IRTS.CodegenCommon, IRTS.DumpBC

